  <section>
    <title>How to get involved</title> 

    <para>
      Helping us is very easy. We provide a list of open tasks we want
      to get solved. Before you jump on our wiki page, consider doing the
      following things before getting started: 
    </para>

    <orderedlist>
     <listitem>
       <para>
         Join our mailinglist at: <ulink
           url='https://mail.gnome.org/mailman/listinfo/gimp-docs-list'
           />
       </para>
      </listitem>
     <listitem>
       <para>Create a local working copy of gimp-help-2 for yourself.</para>
       <para>
         <programlisting>
           <![CDATA[
           $ git clone git://git.gnome.org/gimp-help-2
           ]]>
         </programlisting>
       </para>
     </listitem>
    </orderedlist>
  </section>

</webpage>
